---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — xSoft Ltd | Development Agreements" description="Terms and conditions for using xSoft Ltd services and websites. Clear, fair terms for software development engagements." keywords="terms of service, xSoft, software development terms, consultancy agreement">

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Terms of Service",
    "url": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com/terms/",
    "description": "Terms and conditions for xSoft Ltd services.",
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "xSoft Ltd", "url": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com" },
    "dateModified": "2026-07-15"
  })} />

  <section class="pt-10 pb-8 border-b border-gray-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="animate-fade-in-up text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-white">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="animate-fade-in-delay-1 mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: 15 July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Agreement</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">By using any website or service operated by xSoft Ltd ("we", "us", "our"), you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use our services.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Our Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">xSoft Ltd provides software development consultancy services including but not limited to:</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> AI chatbot development and deployment</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Web application development</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Chrome extension development</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> SEO and content strategy services</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Free-to-use online tools (converters, calculators, games)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Client Engagements</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">For paid development work:</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> <strong>Pricing:</strong> Quoted per project or at £1,000/week. Final scope agreed in writing before work begins.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> <strong>Payment:</strong> 50% upfront, 50% on delivery. Invoices payable within 14 days.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> <strong>Ownership:</strong> Upon full payment, all deliverables (code, designs, documentation) become your property.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> <strong>Support:</strong> 30 days of post-delivery support included. Extended support available.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> <strong>Cancellation:</strong> Either party may cancel with 7 days written notice. Work completed to date is billable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Free Tools & Websites</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Our free tools (ScrabbleWordsFinder, xConvert24, xCrypto24) are provided "as-is" without warranty. We make reasonable efforts to keep them available and accurate but cannot guarantee uninterrupted service or perfect accuracy. Use for entertainment and reference purposes — not as the sole basis for critical decisions.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">All content on xSoft websites (code, design, text, images) is owned by xSoft Ltd unless otherwise stated. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without written permission.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-3">For client work: upon full payment, all custom code and deliverables transfer to you. We retain the right to use anonymised case studies and screenshots for portfolio purposes unless you request otherwise.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">To the maximum extent permitted by law, xSoft Ltd shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of our services or websites. Our total liability for any claim shall not exceed the fees paid by you in the 12 months preceding the claim.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English courts.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:info@xsoftlimited.com" class="text-indigo-400 hover:underline">info@xsoftlimited.com</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
